HEADWORD: Pentastichous
<hw>Pen*tas"ti*chous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Penta-</ets> + Gr. <grk>sti`chos</grk> a row.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having, or arranged in, five vertical ranks, as
the leaves of an apple tree or a cherry tree.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pentastomida</ent>⟦br⟧
